Sentencas: Suspension plasma spraying (SPS) was employed to prepare La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 (LSM) cathode for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: LSM powder in the nanometer size range synthesized by the glycine-nitrate processing (GNP) was used as precursor.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: The surface morphology and microstructure of the LSM deposits were characterized by scanning electron microscopy and x-ray diffraction.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: The influence of spray distance on SPS LSM microstructure was examined.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: The electrochemical behavior was analyzed through the impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: The fine starting particles resulted in a fine microstructure of SPS LSM deposit.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: The results showed that the microstructure of SPS LSM cathode exhibits significant influence on the cathode polarization.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: The improved melting degree of LSM particles during spray deposition leads to reduction of the cathode polarization.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying

Sentencas: The specific surface resistance of 0.45 Omega cm(2) was obtained at 950 degrees C for SPS LSM cathode deposited at a spraying distance of 70 mm.
Titulo: Effect of microstructures on electrochemical behavior of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 deposited by suspension plasma spraying
